    ---------  HELP  -------- for more information, visit http://wayterm.nerocrux.org/ --------

    wayterm > l  or list      /[limit]           # show my timeline with count of [limit], default: 20
    wayterm > p  or profile   /[username]        # show [username]'s profile, default: my profile
    wayterm > t  or tweet     /[text]            # post [text] to my timeline
    wayterm > rc or rcomment  /[tweet_id]        # list [tweet_id]'s comments
    wayterm > c  or comment   /[tweet_id]/[text] # comment to [tweet_id]'s tweet with [text]

